      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Here, we report the isolation and characterization of an operon from T. litoralis, which codes for a complex that is composed of subunits which show high sequence similarity to the components of the non-energy-conserving formate hydrogenlyase (formate dehydrogenase coupled hydrogenase complex, FDH-MHY) system of E. coli [CITATION_1] ."
